{"title":"Ratio Makes DIY Upgrades to 12-speed Even More Affordable with 2x12SH Kit","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ratio-2x12sh-upgrade-kit/","date":1698310800000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit, SRAM mechanical Rival shifting a Shimano 12sp cassette\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_mechanical-Rival-updated-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Making the leap from old SRAM 11-speed to modern 12-speed road just got cheaper AND one step simpler, thanks to this new Ratio  2x12SH Upgrade Kit. Ratio already created the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ration-2x12-road-upgrade-kit/\" target=\"_blank\">lightest 2×12 groupset</a> out of your old SRAM Red. But now you can go 12sp without needing to switch to a new freehub body. All thanks to Ratio and new Shimano 12-speed cassette compatibility…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit from SRAM 11sp to 12sp Shimano</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit, mashup road SRAM 11sp and Shimano 12sp groupsets into SRAmano 12, update your old rim brake road bike to the latest gearing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_update-your-old-rim-brake-bike-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Ratio)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve loved what Ratio has been doing since their first time we saw their 3D-printed stainless steel ratchet that converted 11speed  SRAM road shifters <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ratio-diy-mullet-12-speed-kit-converts-11sp-sram-mechanical-to-shift-eagle-derailleurs/\" target=\"_blank\">to operate an Eagle mountain bike derailleur</a>. Their simple creation gave new life to a lot of old gear. Especially as more roadies and cyclocross riders headed further off track on gravel adventures. More recently, Ratio made another road-focused upgrade kit. That converted SRAM 11 to SRAM 12 – likely creating the lightest 2×12 road groupset possible, thanks to the lightness of the original mechanical Red 22 group. But it required buying their upgrade kit, plus a SRAM 12-speed AXS cassette, a flattop chain, flattop-compatible chainrings, AND most importantly switching from your old HG freehub body to a new SRAM XD-R driver body. Most but not all wheels could be changed over.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit, mashup road SRAM 11sp and Shimano 12sp groupsets into SRAmano 12, on old HG freehub body\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_on-old-HG-freehub-body-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, now you get to stick with your old-school Shimano HG freehub…</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new? SRAmano 12sp!</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit, mashup road SRAM 11sp and Shimano 12sp groupsets into SRAmano 12, Force &amp; Rival group updated\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_Rival-Force-group-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The secret of the new Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit converting SRAM 11 to 12 upgrade is actually Shimano. You see, the latest Shimano 12-speed road groupsets still use their old HG freehub standard. So, by popular demand from their customers, Ratio went back to the drawing board. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit, 3d-printed stainless steel ratchet for SRAM-to-Shimano conversion\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_d-printed-ratchet-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, they’ve created a new internal ratchet that upgrades your SRAM 11sp shifter to match the exact spacing of a Shimano 12sp cassette. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>How-To: What do you need?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Simply open up you old SRAM shifter, swap in the new ratchet, and you are good to go. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Out back you will also need to swap in the new derailleur pulleys into your exiting SRAM derailleur. Because Ratio says, “<em>the geometry of Shimano 12 speed road cassettes means it is necessary to use a slightly offset jockey wheel in order to properly engage the largest sprocket.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit, mashup road SRAM 11sp and Shimano 12sp groupsets into SRAmano 12, new derailleur pulleys\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-pulleys-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part of this upgrade is that is less wasteful – requiring you to dispose of fewer usable parts. And that means it will be cheaper in the end, as well. The Shimano 12-speed cassette fits on your existing Shimano HG 11 freehub body. And the Shimano 12-speed chain still works with your existing 2×11 chainrings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Huzzah! </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit – Pricing, compatibility &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio 2x12SH Upgrade Kit contents\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, the next time your 11sp SRAM chain and cassette need to be replaced, why not make the leap to 12sp? The kit itself sells for just under £100 directly from Ratio now. That includes the ratchet &amp; its mounting bolt, plus a new pair of slightly offset derailleur pulleys optimized for Shimano 12sp chains &amp; cassettes. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3.jpg\" alt=\"Ratio mashup road SRAM 11sp and Shimano 12sp groupsets into SRAmano 12, upgrade old rim brake road bikes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Ratio-2x12SH-Upgrade-Kit_mashup-road-SRAM-11sp-and-Shimano-12sp-groupsets-into-SRAmano-12_new-life-to-old-Cervelo-S3-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The kit will upgrade any of SRAM’s 2×11 generation mechanical road shifters. Red, Force, Rival, or Apex – or even SRAM 10sp shifters if you add another internal upgrade Ratio offers. Then you just need a new Shimano 12sp cassette &amp; chain – Dura-Ace, Ultegra, or 105 – which will work with your current chainrings and HG-equipped wheel.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Easy, peasy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://ratiotechnology.com/product/2x12sh-upgrade-kit/\" target=\"_blank\">RatioTechnology.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ratio-2x12sh-upgrade-kit/\">Ratio Makes DIY Upgrades to 12-speed Even More Affordable with 2x12SH Kit</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"4c691f07ac5bf24c07a7c707374433ae7c6ec9240d6d227da7f4301f479c93ff","category":"Cycling"}